{
  "stem": "10588.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not everybody experiences at the same time, because we were not the same people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So everybody's experience is different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, some became Partisans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some were in the resistance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And our upbringing, we didn't want to leave our parents alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Children didn't want to leave elders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Also, we were told to hurt somebody like us not menschlich, so how can you go kill, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, later on people started to realize that what's happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the beginning, nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a very well kept secret.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the whole idea, because-- excuse me-- for instance before the Holocaust, somebody comes and they wanted you to become-- apostatize.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew-- you knew what they wanted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could say yes or no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes [INAUDIBLE] say, although, historically they could be killed for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But here you didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was a well-kept secret.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was completely unique in history, it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyhow, under those conditions, horrible conditions-- and I'm not going into much of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That alone is so much suffering that it's unbelievable to see how many people died in the ghetto of starvation, of illnesses, and the suffering of the little children and the old people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many times.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Many times my parents would take and-- and I myself-- I would give to my little sister and brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we thought, they're younger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while the grandmother was alive, we always protected the grandmother first.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But unfortunately she-- unfortunately and fortunately, she died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, on November-- the night of November 17, 1942, the Nazis told us we're going to be resettled to a better place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we going or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave us this time a little more bread, and we were so happy [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
